00:40:35,038 --> 00:40:35,983
That’s not it, son.

538
00:40:36,416 --> 00:40:36,896
Pleng.

539
00:40:37,674 --> 00:40:38,560
That’s not it.

540
00:40:39,570 --> 00:40:40,545
I love you.

541
00:40:41,189 --> 00:40:42,320
That’s not what it is, Pleng.

542
00:40:53,545 --> 00:40:54,395
But I hate

543
00:40:58,485 --> 00:40:59,983
I hate murderers like you guys.

544
00:41:03,361 --> 00:41:04,605
I hate this family.

